Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:44.18,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2 years have passed since the \NWar of the Best in Marineford.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and his crew each \Ncompleted individual training
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and returned to Sabaody Archipelago
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.67,0:03:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to go on to the next stage - the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is Soul King?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, about Brook.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He might not...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...come back to do pirating again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.33,0:03:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Grove #46.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.26,0:03:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rookies who have joined the \NStraw Hats keep showing up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.59,0:03:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see some captains.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Big Guns Assembled! The Danger \Nof the Fake Straw Hats!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,45 degrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:04:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Here you go, sir!\N--Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sinks into my bones...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:35.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,SABAODY ARCHIPELAGO GROVE #46
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:35.81,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Grove #46.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:40.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A MEETING SPOT FOR THE STRAW HATS
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are more than 100 pirates here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.32,0:05:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they all work for Straw \NHat Luffy, it's gonna be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong?! Answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:05:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad news!  Tell the backup to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.58,0:06:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.24,0:06:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering who you were, \Nbut you're a Navy soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh gee!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.63,0:06:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Oh! Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that you just informed the Navy-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.06,0:06:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.17,0:06:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a Navy soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I haven't called them yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just about to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, I don't want you to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, there's gonna be blood all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and your friends' blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.55,0:06:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it right, Coribou?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! I'm sorry, brother, I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:07:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.94,0:07:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No that way, you dumb fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caribou, the Navy soldier killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He did it!\N--He's true to his reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, gods, have mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This silly Navy soldier tried to reach \Nhis weapon and attempted to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:08:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please have mercy on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.53,0:08:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, gods, I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bury him, Coribou!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bury this sinful Navy soldier alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I dig, I dig...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.81,0:08:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a minute! Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't call for the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, Caribou!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just dispose of that small-time \NNavy soldier somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.84,0:08:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes Captain Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, look around you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably don't know each other
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you are all gonna \Nwork for me from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a crewmember of the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means when I become \Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're gonna be a shipmate of the King!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To make that happen, from now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you guys should wait on me hand and foot
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.13,0:09:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and fight for me at the \Nrisk of your own life!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a dream to work under
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.85,0:09:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the unheard-of pirate \Nwho caused trouble at...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.13,0:09:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...all of the 3 strongholds of the World \NGovernment: Enies Lobby, Impel Down, Navy HQ!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.43,0:09:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be one of the strongest candidates \Nfor the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what they call \N"getting on the bandwagon"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.72,0:09:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most of them are here already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't wait to see everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We asked you to assemble here because...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I've had my honor insulted - your \Nbig boss who is important to you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The perpetrators have to be somewhere \Nhere on this archipelago!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to find them and drag them to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Consider it done, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.81,0:10:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive those fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, people change a lot in 2 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys don't talk much now, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This mustache guy knows the \Nreal Straw Hats as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know but he'll notice so don't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we gotta do is take him to Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.33,0:10:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't think you two \Nwere ever so friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe 2 years has changed all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your looks have changed also.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.98,0:10:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys wearing disguises too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:10:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Encore! Encore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Encore! Encore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Encore! Encore! Encore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. The Navy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul King, come on now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need a little more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... My fans are calling for an encore...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and they won't stop so I'll go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waiting, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is something that \NI have to tell you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I, Soul King, will...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it! The show is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy? Why are they here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The acting captain of the Rumbar \NPirates - "Humming Swordsman" Brook.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A 33 million berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.95,0:12:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We suspect that you're this pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition to that,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we have information that you're \Nworking for Straw Hats Luffy now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul King Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.81,0:12:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Pirate Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're under arrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Brook-sama is not...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul King is a criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a pirate?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I heard Straw Hat Luffy was dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.41,0:13:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over, Brook.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that you guys might be behind this,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.78,0:13:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was shocking to me when \Nyou told me honestly
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about your retirement backstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.15,0:13:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've became very popular so we \Nwere about to make a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You betrayed us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And our company will be out of business.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's die together, Soul King.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:04.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,GROVE #17 THE ISLAND \NWHERE THE SUNNY IS DOCKED
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?! His body is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're like a robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you shoot beams or missiles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can you transform into?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! With the dreams and enthusiasm \Nof men riding on his back,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he goes into action now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.99,0:14:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Armored Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robot! Robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.82,0:14:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Chopper!  Too much \Nexcitement could kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Franky,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can't do detail work with \Nthose huge hands, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:14:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! A hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hand came out from a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.45,0:15:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.08,0:15:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.75,0:15:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with his body?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is the coating?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Press my nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nose?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Press it for a long time. \NMore than 3 seconds...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please press the nose \Nfor more than 3 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He tried to sound like a robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exciting! Exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2, 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hair...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you set your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wow!\N--Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nami! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.21,0:15:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.03,0:16:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was he doing for 2 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.61,0:16:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I see your weapon? Can I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! That's the main event - \Nyou gotta wait for Luffy-mecha.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.08,0:16:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He moved like a robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said "mecha" at the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.24,0:16:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rayleigh-san! Shakky!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to interrupt your reunion but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there are things going \Non on this archipelago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.71,0:16:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop your instrument and \Nput your hands in the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Band.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Backup singers and dancers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to support me for one more song!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.05,0:16:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My music's got power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:16:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you insane?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over for you, Brook.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Manager, thank you for everything \Nduring the past 2 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And thank you for bringing \Nme here to this archipelago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.50,0:17:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a sad memory of losing \Na fight on this archipelago
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.87,0:17:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this is where we start again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a musician.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My role in the Straw Hats is \Nto make the journey more fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People think Straw Hat Luffy is dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell this to the whole world!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pirate - Straw Hat Luffy is alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He will become the King \Nof the Pirates someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Head Office, can you hear \Nme? I have some big news!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His departure shouldn't \Nbe a quiet one! Oh baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.44,0:18:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul King!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love me to the bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.08,0:18:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll dedicate this to my dear friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to my last soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.75,0:18:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.50,0:18:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san, let's go to the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! I said the show is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.68,0:18:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us hear one more song!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let him sing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right! We don't care who he really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Music is always on my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2, 3, 4...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"New World"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.71,0:18:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.56,0:19:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the story of a hero
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The story of a man who will become king
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.10,0:19:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In war there are no "do-overs"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he stands firm with \Nsandals on his bare feet
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.74,0:19:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.46,0:19:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreamers always struggle
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because sometimes their \Ndreams are out of reach
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.18,0:19:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to live through the days in \Nwhich you have to battle your own demons
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.03,0:19:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a big dream that seems quite a handful
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.05,0:20:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when he mentioned it, \NI could see it coming true
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is the day We got tired of waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.36,0:20:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need nights because \Nwe're short-tempered
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.53,0:20:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is the day It's a great day
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.34,0:20:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kick the clock that was stopped
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.58,0:20:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the New world For the New world
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the New world The world is gonna change
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.31,0:21:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I let him get away because of you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.67,0:21:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a money spinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they think that the fake Straw Hats
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.78,0:21:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are the real ones and \Nhave started mobilizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wiretapped them so there is no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.25,0:21:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told Brook-chan what's going \Non through the Transponder Snail
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.70,0:21:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the venue.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.89,0:21:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's on his way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so he's gonna abandon stardom?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.48,0:21:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has backbone as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-chan, you're a navigator, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.95,0:21:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you how to operate \Nthe coated ship so remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.91,0:21:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.41,0:21:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:21:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.65,0:21:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It got tense all of the sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.53,0:21:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Rayleigh, Luffy is not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.08,0:22:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.84,0:22:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.30,0:22:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.34,0:22:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me big boss, fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.51,0:22:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't find the real pet but \Nisn't he the guy you're looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.21,0:22:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.14,0:22:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy is here already!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.72,0:22:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.11,0:22:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave Sanji a Baby Transponder \NSnail when he came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.28,0:22:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's with Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's good because \Nyou guys have to hurry
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.04,0:22:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- the Navy will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.58,0:22:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's only Monkey-chan that we can't reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.34,0:22:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But take this Vivre Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.17,0:22:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will lead him to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.51,0:22:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grove #42 will be perfect - it's on the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.84,0:22:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the ship there and rendezvous!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.60,0:22:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little busy but you \Nall got through these 2 years
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's time for the new journey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.90,0:23:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only Luffy is still missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.68,0:23:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is waiting for the captain's return.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.95,0:23:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Luffy got caught up in battle between
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.68,0:23:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Marines' Pacifistas and \Nthe Fake Straw Hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.76,0:23:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The results of his two years of \Ntraining become apparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.44,0:23:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.94,0:23:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Battle is on! Show Them \NWhat You Got From Training!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.79,0:23:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
